sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户 (Ctrl+V)
    participant Browser as Browser ClipboardEvent
    participant IPC as Electron IPC (main.cjs)
    participant QC as QuickCapture.parseHtmlToItems
    participant FS as resolveFileItem
    participant State as React setCaptured
    participant Submit as handleSubmit
    participant API as /api/requirements
    participant DB as SQLite (main.cjs)
    participant Detail as Requirements.tsx
    participant Renderer as ContentBlockRenderer

    User->>Browser: Ctrl+V 粘贴
    Browser->>Browser: dt.getData('text/plain')
    Browser->>Browser: dt.getData('text/html')
    Browser-->>Browser: dt.items → raw blobs

    alt HTML empty in browser
        Browser->>IPC: readClipboardHTML()
        IPC-->>Browser: html string
    end

    Browser->>QC: parseHtmlToItems(html, plainText, api)

    QC->>QC: ① clean HTML (nbsp, br)
    QC->>QC: ② extract media URLs (imgRx, videoRx, linkRx)

    loop each media URL
        alt data: URL
            QC->>QC: push { type:'image', content:url }
        else http(s) URL
            QC->>QC: push { type:'image', content:url }
        else file:// URL
            QC->>FS: resolveFileItem(url)
            FS->>IPC: readLocalFile(path)
            IPC-->>FS: dataURL or null
            FS-->>QC: CaptureItem or null
        end
    end

    Note over QC: resolvedMedia[] built

    QC->>QC: ③ hasTableOrVideo check

    alt plainText exists AND no table/video
        QC->>QC: Text-based: [图片]/[视频] markers → resolvedMedia
        Note over QC: ✅ resolvedMedia used correctly
    else hasTableOrVideo OR no plainText
        QC->>QC: HTML-only walk()
        Note over QC: 🔴 BREAK: walk() <video> uses raw src
        Note over QC: 🔴 BREAK: resolvedMedia DISCARDED
        loop walk DOM nodes
            alt <img>
                QC->>QC: push { type:'image', content:rawSrc } ⚠
            else <video>
                QC->>QC: push { type:'video', content:rawSrc } 🔴
            else <table>
                QC->>QC: push { type:'table', rows, headers } ✅
            else text node
                QC->>QC: push { type:'text', content }
            end
        end
    end

    QC-->>Browser: CaptureItem[]

    Browser->>Browser: emptyVideos fallback
    Note over Browser: 🔴 walk() videos have non-empty content
    Note over Browser: → fallback NOT triggered for walk() videos

    Browser->>Browser: raw blobs → dataURL
    Browser->>State: setCaptured({ items })

    Note over State: ⚠ UI: no table rendering in preview

    User->>Submit: 点击"提交需求"
    Submit->>Submit: captureItemsToBlocks(finalItems)
    Note over Submit: CaptureItem[] → ContentBlock[]
    Submit->>API: POST { content_blocks: JSON.stringify(blocks) }

    API->>DB: INSERT INTO requirements (..., content_blocks)
    DB-->>API: newId
    API-->>Submit: { success, id }

    Submit->>Detail: refreshMainList()

    Detail->>API: GET /api/requirements/:id
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM requirements WHERE id=?
    DB-->>API: row (content_blocks at index 19)
    API->>API: formatReq: JSON.parse(r[19])
    API-->>Detail: { contentBlocks: ContentBlock[] }

    Detail->>Renderer: <ContentBlockRenderer blocks={blocks} />

    loop each ContentBlock
        alt type='text'
            Renderer->>Renderer: <TextBlock> ✅
        else type='image'
            Renderer->>Renderer: <ImageBlock> ✅
        else type='video'
            Renderer->>Renderer: <VideoBlock> ✅
            Note over Renderer: ⚠ content may be file path, not dataURL
        else type='file'
            Renderer->>Renderer: <FileBlock> ✅
        else type='table'
            Renderer->>Renderer: <TableBlock> ✅
        end
    end
